>\n當司法體制限制唔到執法者<br />\n同我講正義？暗角無比人影到 結果吿唔入呢？開個先例玩撚完喎<br />\n<br />\n當你體驗過路過突然被打 又無得投訴<br />\n如同法律蕩然無存既時候<br />\n你同我講&quot;佢地無做錯到&quot; <br />\n咁我無野講 你都係無錯既 你係醒既 <br />\n可以呀屌"},{"pid":"e26af5e1ba834d46a16cdf1e9f720da4503b2f36","tid":315043,"uid":5893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"Angel方加"},{"pid":"1af7f8526fdf54a3d4ab6e1c56e338e867b8e998","tid":315043,"uid":54223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"臭閪港女垃撚圾"},{"pid":"52632262850d49eea62f0c005168665ca30a7b08","tid":315043,"uid":13448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:12:28.000Z","msg":"警察打我 我去報警<br />\n我講出黎都笑撚左聲"},{"pid":"ba3ae4b93a620f7e5160c5e44d882abbe40a9fc0","tid":315043,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:13:25.000Z","msg":"即係段對話係用黎試佢既？"},{"pid":"2ca5f8484d58b0de8bb7b5ede5d7c4312702c976","tid":315043,"uid":101310,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"人地叫angle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e032e7240ebac6dc9e46207bd2004519abcb84c","tid":315043,"uid":4736,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"ANGLE呀 識唔撚識英文啊 成班盲毛"},{"pid":"aa464fa56d4afda0c76d51808ae22a8e32b87117","tid":315043,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:25:31.000Z","msg":"我可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed30dfa1cfc33d24e41c7dfe60696ddfbb6d53d7","tid":315043,"uid":1858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個好正 30路中女絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07